  { q: 'Is the Keychron Q1 worth the money?', a: 'Yes, if you want a true custom keyboard feel without building one from a kit. The gasket mount, CNC aluminum body, and QMK/VIA support give you a typing experience that rivals $300+ customs for $149. If you only need a basic mechanical keyboard, the Keychron K8 at $84 is the better value — but the Q1 is the right pick if you care about sound, feel, and customization.' },
